        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "speaking through you",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " will be in God’s sight an unpardonable sin, far more heinous than that of prejudiced Pharisees speaking evil against me, the Son of Man, now.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
